articles.author: Angela Dewan, Ella Nilsen
articles.title: As Trump’s win tests the world order, diplomats are fretting over what it means for the planet - CNN
articles.description: America’s allies and foes alike have spent the past five days speculating about what Donald Trump’s re-election will mean for their economies, security and the world’s grinding wars. Climate diplomats gathering for talks Monday are just as anxious.
